title: Fishing Hero Online client.exe
description:
Fishing Hero is a relaxing online adventure that combines elements of RPG, action, MMO and simulation games to create a unique experience.  The game provides many casual moments though it can has many intense moments depending on the fish you are chasing.  Will you choose to sit back and relax or will you go after the big one?

The game features over 800 species of fish to catch, 20+ locations, character customization, upgrade systems and more!
